-- Disney Loses Trial Over `Who Wants to Be a Millionaire' Game Show's Profit
-- Tori Richards
-- 2010-07-07T18:25:42Z
-- http://www.bloomberg.com/news/2010-07-07/disney-loses-trial-over-who-wants-to-be-a-millionaire-game-show-s-profit.html

          
          
             Walt Disney Co. was found liable for
not paying the U.K. creators of “Who Wants to Be a
Millionaire” their share of profits from the quiz show
broadcasted on Disney’s ABC network.  
